Your Success is Our Policy.®
We don’t simply take advantage of opportunities… we build a future with them.

Watch more about AmTrust


















Insurance Agents




As an appointed agent for AmTrust Financial, you'll have access to our easy-to-use online quoting system to help you deliver superior coverage to your customers, while increasing your revenue at the same time.








Small Business Owners




Our focus on small business solutions has never wavered. We offer multiline insurance coverage, including workers’ compensation insurance and commercial lines. Coverages are also available on a monoline basis.








Extended Warranties




We offer a variety of warranty products including payment protection insurance and motor vehicle service contracts, plus consumer and commercial product coverage.








Job Seekers




Our team is dedicated to finding the right people for the right roles here at AmTrust. We look forward to meeting and speaking with you in the future!








